                     <interp inst="t18050424-12-person186" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - Examined by Mr. Gurney. Q. What is the firm of your house; - A.William Smith, sen. 
               <persName id="t18050424-12-person187">
                  William 
                  Smith
               <interp inst="t18050424-12-person187" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18050424-12-person187" type="given" value="William"></interp>
